article_id:717,category_name:News,title_name:A Gift to Prepare for the First Anniversary!,image_path:,message:<div>With the first anniversary coming up at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>, we will send out the following items as a gift. We hope you will use these to enjoy Dragalia Lost!</div><div><br></div><div><strong>■Gift Details</strong></div><div>・Four-leaf clover x30</div><div>Give these to dragons in the Dragon&#39;s Roost to increase your bond, extending your shapeshift time with that dragon and increasing their might.</div><div>Dragons will even give you items in return.</div><div><br></div><div>・Rupies x1,000,000</div><div>Rupies are used when crafting weapons and leveling up facilities.</div><div>Try using the weapons you craft to challenge Advanced Dragon Trials, Void Battles, and raid event boss battles.</div><div><br></div><div>・10 skip tickets x2</div><div>You can use skip tickets in quests such as the main campaign and raid event boss battles.</div><div>When you use skip tickets, it is treated as if you cleared the quest a number of times equal to the number of tickets used, and you will get that many rewards.</div><div>Note: There are some quests where you cannot use skip tickets.</div><div><br></div><div>・Exquisite honey x10</div><div>You can use one exquisite honey to recover 30 stamina.</div><div>Try using it to clear lots of main campaign quests or quests from the active event.</div><div><br></div><div>This gift will be sent to all players who started the game by <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567317600"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Players can claim it from their goodie boxes for up to seven days after reception. If the gift isn&rsquo;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1567317600,update_time1569478051